Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.92,0:00:18.95,yamadas,,0,0,0,,This is the sun
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.95,0:00:21.02,yamadas,,0,0,0,,This is the moon
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.02,0:00:25.07,yamadas,,0,0,0,, すすきの山の ここは地球
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.52,0:00:31.82,yamadas,,0,0,0,,And this is my grandmother
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.55,0:00:55.52,yamadas,,0,0,0,,My, aren't they beautiful!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.72,0:00:58.25,yamadas,,0,0,0,,Well, if it isn't Mrs. Yamada
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.25,0:01:02.72,yamadas,,0,0,0,,I've never seen such magnificent flowers...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.17,0:01:04.72,yamadas,,0,0,0,,Yep, they're like my children
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.17,0:01:06.77,yamadas,,0,0,0,,And what do you call this one?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.77,0:01:08.42,yamadas,,0,0,0,,Ah, this one is Mino Chrysanthemum...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.42,0:01:10.42,yamadas,,0,0,0,,and this one is the large flowering...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.77,0:01:12.80,yamadas,,0,0,0,,Not the flowers, this bug
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.00,0:01:17.57,yamadas,,0,0,0,,Beats me
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.15,0:01:23.12,yamadas,,0,0,0,,Turn into a butterfly as beautiful as this flower, you hear?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.60,0:01:27.85,yamadas,,0,0,0,,Mother!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.57,0:01:31.35,yamadas,,0,0,0,,That's my grandmother
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.87,0:01:44.77,yamadas,,0,0,0,,And this is my mother and me, Nonoko
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.85,0:01:49.92,yamadas,,0,0,0,,What am I going to make for dinner tonight?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.37,0:01:54.70,yamadas,,0,0,0,,I've got it!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.70,0:01:56.05,yamadas,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.05,0:01:57.67,yamadas,,0,0,0,,What are you making?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.77,0:02:00.32,yamadas,,0,0,0,,All last week we had curry, but
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.47,0:02:02.32,yamadas,,0,0,0,,tonight let's do curry!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.50,0:02:18.90,yamadas,,0,0,0,,And this is my father and older brother
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.90,0:02:23.15,yamadas,,0,0,0,,Dad, what's the point of studying this?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.02,0:02:25.55,yamadas,,0,0,0,,Listen, Noboru
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.52,0:02:29.67,yamadas,,0,0,0,,Studying isn't about what's useful or not
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.95,0:02:32.35,yamadas,,0,0,0,,What may seem useless now
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.35,0:02:35.07,yamadas,,0,0,0,,may turn out to be useful
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.50,0:02:37.52,yamadas,,0,0,0,,What I mean is,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.52,0:02:40.20,yamadas,,0,0,0,,useful studying may turn out to be useless
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.30,0:02:43.50,yamadas,,0,0,0,,and useless studying may turn out to be useful
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.65,0:02:45.40,yamadas,,0,0,0,,When it comes in handy
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.40,0:02:48.12,yamadas,,0,0,0,,it's not about whether it's useful or useless
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.12,0:02:51.25,yamadas,,0,0,0,,Seriously, what are you going on about?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.17,0:02:56.45,yamadas,,0,0,0,,I guess it's important after all
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.70,0:03:29.02,yamadas,,0,0,0,,Wow,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.62,0:03:32.87,yamadas,,0,0,0,,If my father was smart and cool
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.97,0:03:36.37,yamadas,,0,0,0,,and my mother was beautiful, stylish, and a good cook
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.65,0:03:40.25,yamadas,,0,0,0,,and we had more money
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.25,0:03:43.40,yamadas,,0,0,0,,my life would have been totally different
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.70,0:03:49.22,yamadas,,0,0,0,,If one of them had...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.22,0:03:51.22,yamadas,,0,0,0,,Don't be stupid
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.75,0:03:55.95,yamadas,,0,0,0,,If we hadn't gotten married, you wouldn't have been born
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.17,0:03:59.77,yamadas,,0,0,0,,If one of us was different, you wouldn't be here
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.07,0:04:01.92,yamadas,,0,0,0,,Not necessarily,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.10,0:04:06.25,yamadas,,0,0,0,,If I'd had different parents I'd just be cooler
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.40,0:04:07.82,yamadas,,0,0,0,,You're ridiculous
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.82,0:04:09.95,yamadas,,0,0,0,,Don't you know about the birds and the bees?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.07,0:04:11.77,yamadas,,0,0,0,,??? you have to sow seeds ???
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.82,0:04:12.82,yamadas,,0,0,0,,That's right
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.90,0:04:14.67,yamadas,,0,0,0,,You can't choose your parents
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.82,0:04:17.20,yamadas,,0,0,0,,I don't believe that
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.20,0:04:19.20,yamadas,,0,0,0,,It just doesn't seem right
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.35,0:04:24.02,yamadas,,0,0,0,,I'm me, dad's dad, and mom's mom, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.87,0:04:26.87,yamadas,,0,0,0,,What's that supposed to mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.40,0:04:30.05,yamadas,,0,0,0,,Who are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.80,0:04:32.97,yamadas,,0,0,0,,Where did I come from?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.00,0:04:35.60,yamadas,,0,0,0,,Where am I?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.40,0:04:38.35,yamadas,,0,0,0,,Who am I?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.85,0:04:41.35,yamadas,,0,0,0,,Whoa,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.87,0:04:46.55,yamadas,,0,0,0,,Mom and dad weren't always married
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.32,0:05:13.37,yamadas,,0,0,0,,In celebration of their new life together
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.37,0:05:18.82,yamadas,,0,0,0,,let's give a heartfelt round of applause to Takashi and Matsuko
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.05,0:05:22.42,yamadas,,0,0,0,,Matsuko, Takashi
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.52,0:05:24.10,yamadas,,0,0,0,,Congratulations
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.32,0:05:27.50,yamadas,,0,0,0,,And to their parents and relatives
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.62,0:05:30.12,yamadas,,0,0,0,,I offer my heartfelt congratulations
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.42,0:05:39.85,yamadas,,0,0,0,, As for you two
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.90,0:05:42.62,yamadas,,0,0,0,, I wish you smooth sailing on your journey
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.60,0:05:44.37,yamadas,,0,0,0,,  across the open seas
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.45,0:05:46.37,yamadas,,0,0,0,, 船出しやはったわけです set sail
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.17,0:06:03.25,yamadas,,0,0,0,, Life has its ups and downs
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.25,0:06:05.25,yamadas,,0,0,0,, 時には 大波になぶられて Especially you will be tormented big waves
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.32,0:06:08.85,yamadas,,0,0,0,,??? (奈落の底にIn the abyss (突き落とされたり…な pushed into（せやけどね) そうだけど
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.85,0:06:11.05,yamadas,,0,0,0,, Don't worry
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.05,0:06:13.17,yamadas,,0,0,0,,Carrying on by oneself and
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.17,0:06:16.02,yamadas,,0,0,0,,seeing things through to the end is admirable, but
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.35,0:06:18.12,yamadas,,0,0,0,,???
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.12,0:06:19.05,yamadas,,0,0,0,,Together,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.05,0:06:21.65,yamadas,,0,0,0,, 大概は 切り抜けられるもんです you can get through most anything
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.42,0:06:26.55,yamadas,,0,0,0,,Isn't that right?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.55,0:06:27.95,yamadas,,0,0,0,,Here's some advice
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.10,0:06:31.00,yamadas,,0,0,0,,Have children as soon as possible
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.87,0:06:34.30,yamadas,,0,0,0,,You can overcome life's troubles
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.30,0:06:37.50,yamadas,,0,0,0,,?? 子供.....と決まっとります
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.97,0:07:49.35,yamadas,,0,0,0,, Nowadays raising kids can seem troublesome
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.35,0:07:51.85,yamadas,,0,0,0,,and difficult, but
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.15,0:07:54.95,yamadas,,0,0,0,, People have been doing it since long ago
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.47,0:07:58.27,yamadas,,0,0,0,,It's said that even without parents, children grow up
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.50,0:07:59.82,yamadas,,0,0,0,,Once they can crawl, they stand
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.82,0:08:01.82,yamadas,,0,0,0,,Once they can stand, they walk
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.90,0:08:03.70,yamadas,,0,0,0,,And when you hold them close,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.70,0:08:05.55,yamadas,,0,0,0,,they can get through most anything
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.02,0:08:19.12,yamadas,,0,0,0,,さて、子を持って知る親の恩
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.97,0:08:23.10,yamadas,,0,0,0,,they think that parents are just annoying, but
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.10,0:08:25.07,yamadas,,0,0,0,,子供は預かって貰えるし they're taken care of,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.07,0:08:27.07,yamadas,,0,0,0,,and, more importantly, bought toys
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.52,0:08:31.15,yamadas,,0,0,0,,子供を持って 初めて 親の.....恩を知った と When you first have kids
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.50,0:08:32.52,yamadas,,0,0,0,,If you make a mistake
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.52,0:08:35.95,yamadas,,0,0,0,, be sure to remember this old saying:
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.50,0:08:37.47,yamadas,,0,0,0,,"Oh, I get it now"
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.47,0:08:39.57,yamadas,,0,0,0,,それも親の恩のうちや
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.47,0:08:41.37,yamadas,,0,0,0,,In other words, うまいこといくと
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.37,0:08:43.37,yamadas,,0,0,0,,親の土地 建物
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.10,0:08:45.37,yamadas,,0,0,0,,当てに できるかもわかりません you don't know if you can count on
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.20,0:08:49.65,yamadas,,0,0,0,,Anyway, Matsuko,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.77,0:08:51.07,yamadas,,0,0,0,,Takashi,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.30,0:08:54.30,yamadas,,0,0,0,,From now on, 今から　親を大事にせな あきまへんで
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.32,0:08:55.75,yamadas,,0,0,0,,For your information
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.75,0:08:57.75,yamadas,,0,0,0,,this land's in my name
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.85,0:08:59.12,yamadas,,0,0,0,,With all due respect,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.35,0:09:01.22,yamadas,,0,0,0,,I built this house
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.22,0:09:03.67,yamadas,,0,0,0,,If there was no land, you couldn't build a house
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.75,0:09:06.80,yamadas,,0,0,0,,And you know I always thank you for that,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.95,0:09:09.30,yamadas,,0,0,0,,but try to see all the hard work I've put in
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.37,0:09:12.32,yamadas,,0,0,0,,Your room gets the best light...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.02,0:09:13.80,yamadas,,0,0,0,,Yeah, thanks a lot
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.90,0:09:15.45,yamadas,,0,0,0,,That's to be expected...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.45,0:09:17.92,yamadas,,0,0,0,,since you built on my land
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.05,0:09:19.35,yamadas,,0,0,0,,Besides, you
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.35,0:09:22.25,yamadas,,0,0,0,,didn't build this house yourself
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.32,0:09:23.57,yamadas,,0,0,0,,Look,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.67,0:09:25.67,yamadas,,0,0,0,,If we're talking about this house, make no mistake, I...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.67,0:09:27.97,yamadas,,0,0,0,,Cut it out, you two!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.02,0:09:29.67,yamadas,,0,0,0,,It's shameful!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.67,0:09:30.87,yamadas,,0,0,0,,That's right!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.00,0:09:33.32,yamadas,,0,0,0,,What's the point of all this fighting?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.45,0:09:35.15,yamadas,,0,0,0,,What he said!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.32,0:09:37.05,yamadas,,0,0,0,,Eventually it will be my house anyway
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.77,0:10:02.77,yamadas,,0,0,0,,By the way,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.77,0:10:04.32,yamadas,,0,0,0,,On the path to a long life
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.32,0:10:06.52,yamadas,,0,0,0,,What's the scariest thing?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.62,0:10:08.27,yamadas,,0,0,0,,A raging storm?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.32,0:10:10.27,yamadas,,0,0,0,,A raging stream?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.30,0:10:18.97,yamadas,,0,0,0,,Actually, in the calmest seas
