Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.10,0:11:28.25,yamadas,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.25,0:11:29.60,yamadas,,0,0,0,,Go right at that corner!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.60,0:11:30.67,yamadas,,0,0,0,,Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.82,0:11:31.95,yamadas,,0,0,0,,Left!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.95,0:11:34.02,yamadas,,0,0,0,,Right up here, no left!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.87,0:11:34.82,yamadas,,0,0,0,,Speak clearly!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.97,0:11:37.07,yamadas,,0,0,0,,Hmm, maybe it was a right.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.07,0:11:38.82,yamadas,,0,0,0,,Which is it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.10,0:11:49.07,yamadas,,0,0,0,,We almost had it
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.07,0:11:50.47,yamadas,,0,0,0,,Our turn!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.47,0:11:52.45,yamadas,,0,0,0,,The breakdown of the family
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.67,0:12:02.17,yamadas,,0,0,0,,Is this some kind of detour?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.20,0:12:03.90,yamadas,,0,0,0,,Turn at this light
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.95,0:12:05.40,yamadas,,0,0,0,,No, straight! Go straight!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.40,0:12:07.60,yamadas,,0,0,0,,It's over there. What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.67,0:12:09.60,yamadas,,0,0,0,,Dad, we should have gone this way
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.52,0:12:10.52,yamadas,,0,0,0,,Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.72,0:12:12.15,yamadas,,0,0,0,,???
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.02,0:12:15.67,yamadas,,0,0,0,,The only one who's being quiet is Nonoko
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.80,0:12:17.40,yamadas,,0,0,0,,Oh
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.60,0:12:19.40,yamadas,,0,0,0,,She's not in the car
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.37,0:12:21.90,yamadas,,0,0,0,,Nonoko?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.07,0:12:23.52,yamadas,,0,0,0,,Why's she not in the car?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.52,0:12:25.52,yamadas,,0,0,0,,Well anyway, stop the car!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.15,0:12:32.62,yamadas,,0,0,0,,Where'd we leave her?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.62,0:12:33.95,yamadas,,0,0,0,,Noboru,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.95,0:12:36.25,yamadas,,0,0,0,,Weren't you with Nonoko?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.25,0:12:39.62,yamadas,,0,0,0,,Yea, with Dad while we waited on you guys.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.00,0:12:42.82,yamadas,,0,0,0,,Maybe she got bored and wandered off
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.82,0:12:45.15,yamadas,,0,0,0,,No way, she was sitting on the bench with us
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.62,0:12:54.70,yamadas,,0,0,0,,Thanks for waiting
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.12,0:12:57.40,yamadas,,0,0,0,, Took you long enough!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.60,0:13:00.42,yamadas,,0,0,0,,Sorry, I thought we'd be finished soon
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.52,0:13:02.77,yamadas,,0,0,0,,I had places I wanted to go
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.10,0:13:05.87,yamadas,,0,0,0,,We won't have enough time to go to the sports store!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.87,0:13:07.87,yamadas,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.87,0:13:09.87,yamadas,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.87,0:13:11.27,yamadas,,0,0,0,,That's it!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.47,0:13:13.27,yamadas,,0,0,0,,It must have been there!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.40,0:13:23.97,yamadas,,0,0,0,,It's your fault for rushing us
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.05,0:13:25.17,yamadas,,0,0,0,,It's not my fault!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.02,0:13:27.40,yamadas,,0,0,0,,You never have to wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.40,0:13:31.40,yamadas,,0,0,0,,In all the excitement she got left behind
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.40,0:13:32.92,yamadas,,0,0,0,,Poor thing...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.92,0:13:36.32,yamadas,,0,0,0,,What are you talking about? Like it's somebody else's problem
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.52,0:13:39.65,yamadas,,0,0,0,,Weren't we looking at clothes for you?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.72,0:13:42.70,yamadas,,0,0,0,,The sports store is closed! We missed it!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.70,0:13:45.12,yamadas,,0,0,0,,You're just thinking about yourself
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.22,0:13:48.77,yamadas,,0,0,0,,If it was you, how would you feel?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.87,0:13:51.10,yamadas,,0,0,0,,What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.45,0:13:54.37,yamadas,,0,0,0,,Maybe...she was kidnapped?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.12,0:13:59.82,yamadas,,0,0,0,,かわいいやろ わたしに似て
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.95,0:14:03.62,yamadas,,0,0,0,,This is no laughing matter!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.62,0:14:07.42,yamadas,,0,0,0,,In this situation, one thing could be of some help
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.37,0:14:08.72,yamadas,,0,0,0,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.85,0:14:11.17,yamadas,,0,0,0,,The PTA slogan:
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.40,0:14:15.27,yamadas,,0,0,0,,"If a stranger talks to you, use caution!"
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.27,0:14:18.07,yamadas,,0,0,0,,Are they teaching such stupid things to children?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.15,0:14:21.70,yamadas,,0,0,0,,Then you just think everyone is a thief
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.77,0:14:24.40,yamadas,,0,0,0,,With those teeth, she'll be fine
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.42,0:14:26.72,yamadas,,0,0,0,, Cake!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.05,0:14:28.62,yamadas,,0,0,0,,Gimme some!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.62,0:14:30.42,yamadas,,0,0,0,,Ok, just one bite
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.42,0:14:31.47,yamadas,,0,0,0,,Ok
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.50,0:14:34.95,yamadas,,0,0,0,,She'll bite them for sure!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.95,0:14:36.32,yamadas,,0,0,0,,Idiot
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.80,0:14:42.42,yamadas,,0,0,0,,Will you let me in?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.42,0:14:44.42,yamadas,,0,0,0,,I think my daughter's been abducted
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.40,0:14:49.92,yamadas,,0,0,0,,We need to call them
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.92,0:14:51.92,yamadas,,0,0,0,,We should have called earlier...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.62,0:14:54.25,yamadas,,0,0,0,,That's why we should have cell phones
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.25,0:14:56.25,yamadas,,0,0,0,,You be quiet!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.90,0:15:00.92,yamadas,,0,0,0,,Poor Nonoko!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.65,0:15:29.12,yamadas,,0,0,0,,Are you lost?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.60,0:15:31.77,yamadas,,0,0,0,,Umm...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.95,0:15:34.22,yamadas,,0,0,0,,Are you waiting on someone?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.87,0:15:43.35,yamadas,,0,0,0,,Who are you waiting for?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.57,0:15:47.65,yamadas,,0,0,0,,Can't you talk?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.92,0:15:50.20,yamadas,,0,0,0,,Why aren't you saying anything?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.65,0:15:52.47,yamadas,,0,0,0,,You're a stranger...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.72,0:15:55.97,yamadas,,0,0,0,,I can't talk to you
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.12,0:16:03.12,yamadas,,0,0,0,,That's right. "Use caution when talking to strangers." That thing?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.67,0:16:05.50,yamadas,,0,0,0,,You're great!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.50,0:16:09.37,yamadas,,0,0,0,,用心したもん もうお話しても大丈夫だよ
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.97,0:16:12.07,yamadas,,0,0,0,,Wow, you're really great
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.35,0:16:17.30,yamadas,,0,0,0,,My father, mother, grandma and older brother are all lost
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.50,0:16:19.40,yamadas,,0,0,0,,Did you get separated from someone?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.55,0:16:20.80,yamadas,,0,0,0,,Yeah,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.05,0:16:22.62,yamadas,,0,0,0,,my mom...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.62,0:16:24.00,yamadas,,0,0,0,,Your mom!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.05,0:16:28.32,yamadas,,0,0,0,,Mom's gone...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.32,0:16:32.52,yamadas,,0,0,0,,Wow, I guess lost parents are getting common
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.97,0:16:36.50,yamadas,,0,0,0,,But it's just your mother, you'll find her soon!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.10,0:16:43.30,yamadas,,0,0,0,,Excuse me,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.30,0:16:47.90,yamadas,,0,0,0,,This is Kimura Toshio. Can you call his mother?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.02,0:16:48.85,yamadas,,0,0,0,,Lost, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.85,0:16:50.92,yamadas,,0,0,0,,Not lost, just separated
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.92,0:16:54.72,yamadas,,0,0,0,,Oh I see
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.10,0:16:58.07,yamadas,,0,0,0,,Let's see. Mr. Kimura, what's your first name?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.12,0:16:59.35,yamadas,,0,0,0,,Toshio!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.35,0:17:01.35,yamadas,,0,0,0,,Toshio, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.35,0:17:04.90,yamadas,,0,0,0,,Ok, please wait here a moment
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.42,0:17:09.40,yamadas,,0,0,0,,And who are you? The older sister?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.62,0:17:11.20,yamadas,,0,0,0,,Nope
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.20,0:17:14.12,yamadas,,0,0,0,,My whole family got lost
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.62,0:17:31.45,yamadas,,0,0,0,,♪ Little lost Koneko ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.45,0:17:33.55,yamadas,,0,0,0,,♪ Where did you come -- ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.42,0:17:43.42,yamadas,,0,0,0,,Don't cry. We're here
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.30,0:18:14.45,yamadas,,0,0,0,,What do you mean she went with her mother?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.45,0:18:16.87,yamadas,,0,0,0,,I'm her mother!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.35,0:18:18.42,yamadas,,0,0,0,,Is that so?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.42,0:18:21.77,yamadas,,0,0,0,,あんた　ようもウチの子を
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.77,0:18:25.35,yamadas,,0,0,0,,Maybe it wasn't her mother, but it seemed like someone she knew
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.45,0:18:26.82,yamadas,,0,0,0,,Someone she knew?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.82,0:18:27.87,yamadas,,0,0,0,,Who could it be?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.87,0:18:30.47,yamadas,,0,0,0,,I have no idea
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.52,0:18:34.32,yamadas,,0,0,0,,知り合いのようなフリして
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.32,0:18:38.17,yamadas,,0,0,0,,No, she was called by her mother
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.20,0:18:39.42,yamadas,,0,0,0,,It wasn't her mother!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.42,0:18:40.32,yamadas,,0,0,0,,Don't make a fuss!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.80,0:18:42.12,yamadas,,0,0,0,,And then?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.20,0:18:44.80,yamadas,,0,0,0,,They apologized
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.80,0:18:51.70,yamadas,,0,0,0,,And then Nonoko left happily with the person who was like her mother
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.82,0:18:54.67,yamadas,,0,0,0,,Who could it be?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.72,0:18:56.67,yamadas,,0,0,0,,Anyhow, can you call for Nonoko?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.97,0:19:00.55,yamadas,,0,0,0,,Well, the two of them walked out of that exit
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.55,0:19:01.42,yamadas,,0,0,0,,She's not there.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.42,0:19:03.17,yamadas,,0,0,0,,Come on!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.87,0:19:10.22,yamadas,,0,0,0,,I wonder what happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.20,0:19:21.92,yamadas,,0,0,0,,Dad, where are we going in such a hurry?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.92,0:19:23.32,yamadas,,0,0,0,,We're in pursuit
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.32,0:19:24.07,yamadas,,0,0,0,,Of what?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.07,0:19:26.72,yamadas,,0,0,0,,Isn't it obvious? The car Nonoko's in
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.87,0:19:28.10,yamadas,,0,0,0,,What kind of car is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.62,0:19:37.60,yamadas,,0,0,0,,Oh, which way did they go?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.95,0:19:39.15,yamadas,,0,0,0,,It's OK
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.15,0:19:41.27,yamadas,,0,0,0,,It was some lady that knew Nonoko, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.05,0:19:43.52,yamadas,,0,0,0,,She'll take her home
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.85,0:19:46.77,yamadas,,0,0,0,,He's got a point
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.27,0:19:49.90,yamadas,,0,0,0,,Yes, that's it!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.80,0:19:53.17,yamadas,,0,0,0,,Don't be so naive. The person she knows could be dangerous
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.42,0:19:54.62,yamadas,,0,0,0,,Mom!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.65,0:19:58.22,yamadas,,0,0,0,,警察に届けたら ええやろな
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.22,0:19:59.30,yamadas,,0,0,0,,The police!?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.27,0:20:01.35,yamadas,,0,0,0,,Why on Earth are you talking about this?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.40,0:20:03.42,yamadas,,0,0,0,,Just telling you the truth
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.72,0:20:04.62,yamadas,,0,0,0,,The truth?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.67,0:20:07.80,yamadas,,0,0,0,,Four adults neglecting a young girl
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.80,0:20:10.07,yamadas,,0,0,0,,The abandoned child was eaten
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.75,0:20:13.22,yamadas,,0,0,0,,Does Nonoko have a key?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.62,0:20:15.77,yamadas,,0,0,0,,Let's go home!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.70,0:20:48.85,yamadas,,0,0,0,,Nonoko!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.67,0:20:51.35,yamadas,,0,0,0,,Nonoko!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.97,0:20:55.30,yamadas,,0,0,0,,Nonoko!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.72,0:21:00.10,yamadas,,0,0,0,,Nonoko!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.97,0:21:07.75,yamadas,,0,0,0,,当たり前や 閉まっとったんやから
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.17,0:21:14.95,yamadas,,0,0,0,,Hello? This is Mrs. Yamada
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.75,0:21:18.27,yamadas,,0,0,0,,Oh thank goodness!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.27,0:21:22.55,yamadas,,0,0,0,,I can't thank you enough!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.82,0:21:26.75,yamadas,,0,0,0,,Oh no, no, we were looking all over
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.67,0:21:29.62,yamadas,,0,0,0,,Sorry for all the trouble
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.67,0:21:32.42,yamadas,,0,0,0,,Could you bring her over soon?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.42,0:21:35.75,yamadas,,0,0,0,,No, no, we'll come get her
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.82,0:21:39.02,yamadas,,0,0,0,,And you even fed her dinner!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.12,0:21:42.07,yamadas,,0,0,0,,That's so kind of you
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.07,0:21:45.37,yamadas,,0,0,0,,I don't know how to thank you...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.70,0:21:51.07,yamadas,,0,0,0,,At last I got through to them
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.07,0:21:52.85,yamadas,,0,0,0,,Seems like they just got back
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.87,0:21:55.60,yamadas,,0,0,0,,She'll be here soon to pick you up
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.70,0:21:57.55,yamadas,,0,0,0,,Sorry, auntie
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.70,0:21:59.62,yamadas,,0,0,0,,It's nothing!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.67,0:22:04.90,yamadas,,0,0,0,,I love to hear what's going on with the Yamada family
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.55,0:22:21.07,yamadas,,0,0,0,,秋の夜を　打崩したる　咄かな -- Basho
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.32,0:22:27.80,yamadas,,0,0,0,,Blue sky
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.80,0:22:31.95,yamadas,,0,0,0,,white clouds
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.95,0:22:34.47,yamadas,,0,0,0,,そのうち なんとか
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.52,0:22:38.00,yamadas,,0,0,0,,なるだろう
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.72,0:23:05.85,yamadas,,0,0,0,,Approaching Ichinin-mae
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.82,0:23:10.70,yamadas,,0,0,0,,The bus will stop at the next stop
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.45,0:23:16.35,yamadas,,0,0,0,,What stop was it?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.85,0:23:19.92,yamadas,,0,0,0,,For now don't push the button, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.95,0:23:24.92,yamadas,,0,0,0,,家政の天才
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.57,0:23:27.90,yamadas,,0,0,0,,It started raining
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.52,0:23:36.52,yamadas,,0,0,0,,I left the laundry out!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.57,0:23:42.30,yamadas,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.92,0:23:50.32,yamadas,,0,0,0,,What'd you say?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.95,0:23:58.22,yamadas,,0,0,0,,Oh yeah! I brought it in already
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.22,0:24:00.85,yamadas,,0,0,0,,No, you forgot to hang it!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.05,0:24:03.55,yamadas,,0,0,0,,I'm stepping out for a bit
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.72,0:24:05.40,yamadas,,0,0,0,,Need anything from the store?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.57,0:24:08.32,yamadas,,0,0,0,,Ah, there was something...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.67,0:24:10.67,yamadas,,0,0,0,,Oh what was it?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.67,0:24:17.42,yamadas,,0,0,0,,Well, I'm going
Dialogue: 0,0:24:19.55,0:24:23.32,yamadas,,0,0,0,,We needed...oh what was it?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:26.85,0:24:28.55,yamadas,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:34.77,0:24:36.42,yamadas,,0,0,0,,W-w-wait a second!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:36.42,0:24:38.42,yamadas,,0,0,0,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:41.52,0:24:44.22,yamadas,,0,0,0,, It was, uh, uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:44.42,0:24:46.92,yamadas,,0,0,0,,Get yourself together!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:48.60,0:24:51.10,yamadas,,0,0,0,,Ah! White bread!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:53.90,0:24:56.35,yamadas,,0,0,0,,As you wish!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:56.57,0:24:58.70,yamadas,,0,0,0,,Mom!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:59.62,0:25:01.42,yamadas,,0,0,0,,I'll pay you back!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:02.77,0:25:04.42,yamadas,,0,0,0,,I'm home!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:05.82,0:25:08.62,yamadas,,0,0,0,,Huh, mom's not home?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:10.50,0:25:11.92,yamadas,,0,0,0,,There's udon!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:11.92,0:25:14.52,yamadas,,0,0,0,,And there's water boiling!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:15.47,0:25:17.97,yamadas,,0,0,0,,I'll eat it before anyone notices
Dialogue: 0,0:25:24.00,0:25:27.42,yamadas,,0,0,0,,Oh, welcome home!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:36.20,0:25:38.27,yamadas,,0,0,0,,Were you hiding?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:42.90,0:25:43.90,yamadas,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:45.62,0:25:47.80,yamadas,,0,0,0,,The light is out
Dialogue: 0,0:25:47.80,0:25:50.70,yamadas,,0,0,0,,That's no good, we'll have to change it
Dialogue: 0,0:25:51.95,0:25:53.02,yamadas,,0,0,0,,Darnit
Dialogue: 0,0:25:53.32,0:25:55.02,yamadas,,0,0,0,,I thought we had a spare
Dialogue: 0,0:25:55.10,0:25:58.82,yamadas,,0,0,0,,For now, just switch it with one we rarely use
Dialogue: 0,0:26:05.12,0:26:06.80,yamadas,,0,0,0,,Borrowing this for a bit
Dialogue: 0,0:26:07.25,0:26:08.22,yamadas,,0,0,0,,Ouch!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:12.52,0:26:13.90,yamadas,,0,0,0,,Can I have some tea?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:13.92,0:26:16.07,yamadas,,0,0,0,,Me too!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:16.22,0:26:18.37,yamadas,,0,0,0,,I'm busy with the dishes!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:18.37,0:26:21.00,yamadas,,0,0,0,,One of you get it!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:23.02,0:26:25.72,yamadas,,0,0,0,,Rock, paper, scissors, shoot!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:27.72,0:26:31.20,yamadas,,0,0,0,,Get a cup for yourself
Dialogue: 0,0:26:36.20,0:26:39.17,yamadas,,0,0,0,,And can I get you to finish up the dishes?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:39.30,0:26:40.97,yamadas,,0,0,0,,What??
Dialogue: 0,0:26:41.77,0:26:43.82,yamadas,,0,0,0,,Mr. Tanaka is going to drop by
Dialogue: 0,0:26:44.95,0:26:46.25,yamadas,,0,0,0,,What am I gonna do?!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:49.60,0:26:52.22,yamadas,,0,0,0,,I guess we need to pick up a little
Dialogue: 0,0:27:11.40,0:27:12.15,yamadas,,0,0,0,,What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:12.15,0:27:15.22,yamadas,,0,0,0,,I was cleaning up
Dialogue: 0,0:27:18.67,0:27:19.45,yamadas,,0,0,0,,There we go
Dialogue: 0,0:27:21.50,0:27:23.45,yamadas,,0,0,0,,我が家の夫婦道
Dialogue: 0,0:27:27.62,0:27:30.35,yamadas,,0,0,0,,It's on the kitchen table!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:31.72,0:27:33.47,yamadas,,0,0,0,,I don't see it
Dialogue: 0,0:27:33.65,0:27:35.82,yamadas,,0,0,0,,Look carefully, I know I left it there
Dialogue: 0,0:27:35.97,0:27:37.82,yamadas,,0,0,0,,It's not there
Dialogue: 0,0:27:38.25,0:27:40.15,yamadas,,0,0,0,,Where are you looking?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:40.15,0:27:43.52,yamadas,,0,0,0,,It's an envelope with "OKK" written on it in red
Dialogue: 0,0:27:43.75,0:27:45.77,yamadas,,0,0,0,,Sir, is it this?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:46.90,0:27:50.05,yamadas,,0,0,0,,No, no it's OK.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:51.60,0:27:53.90,yamadas,,0,0,0,,If it's not there, it's not there
Dialogue: 0,0:27:57.52,0:28:00.12,yamadas,,0,0,0,,主婦２０年　ダテじゃないね
Dialogue: 0,0:28:00.22,0:28:01.45,yamadas,,0,0,0,,Can I see the paper?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:01.45,0:28:03.45,yamadas,,0,0,0,,After I'm finished
Dialogue: 0,0:28:05.30,0:28:06.90,yamadas,,0,0,0,,大したもんで
Dialogue: 0,0:28:12.07,0:28:14.07,yamadas,,0,0,0,,Dear,
Dialogue: 0,0:28:14.77,0:28:16.85,yamadas,,0,0,0,,While you're out, can you pick up some things?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:16.87,0:28:17.62,yamadas,,0,0,0,,Sure thing
Dialogue: 0,0:28:18.05,0:28:23.10,yamadas,,0,0,0,,Lettuce, cucumber, ham, light bulbs, and trash bags
Dialogue: 0,0:28:23.27,0:28:24.70,yamadas,,0,0,0,,I'll write it down
Dialogue: 0,0:28:24.70,0:28:27.17,yamadas,,0,0,0,,It's OK, I'll remember
Dialogue: 0,0:28:30.22,0:28:35.85,yamadas,,0,0,0,,Lettuce, cucumber, ham...light bulbs, and trash bags, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:37.05,0:28:40.47,yamadas,,0,0,0,,Did I forget something?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:42.17,0:28:45.65,yamadas,,0,0,0,, Lettuce, cucumber...
Dialogue: 0,0:28:54.42,0:28:55.92,yamadas,,0,0,0,, Hurry up and decide
Dialogue: 0,0:28:55.92,0:28:57.92,yamadas,,0,0,0,,You've already decided?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:58.62,0:29:00.65,yamadas,,0,0,0,,ああ　早くしろってば
Dialogue: 0,0:29:04.07,0:29:06.10,yamadas,,0,0,0,,Oh! Maybe I'll do this Shanghai set lunch
Dialogue: 0,0:29:06.10,0:29:07.22,yamadas,,0,0,0,,Me too
Dialogue: 0,0:29:08.17,0:29:09.77,yamadas,,0,0,0,,Two Shanghai set lunches
Dialogue: 0,0:29:15.67,0:29:18.05,yamadas,,0,0,0,,What are you still doing here?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:18.05,0:29:19.80,yamadas,,0,0,0,,What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:19.80,0:29:22.57,yamadas,,0,0,0,,Can't a husband take a break now and then?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:23.37,0:29:25.95,yamadas,,0,0,0,, It's just that you usually go to the pachinko parlor
Dialogue: 0,0:29:26.05,0:29:27.95,yamadas,,0,0,0,,今日は禁パチ日だ
Dialogue: 0,0:29:28.22,0:29:29.65,yamadas,,0,0,0,,Can I get some tea?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:30.35,0:29:32.55,yamadas,,0,0,0,,I think I'd like udon for lunch
Dialogue: 0,0:29:32.55,0:29:34.25,yamadas,,0,0,0,,Ok, Ok
Dialogue: 0,0:29:36.82,0:29:39.67,yamadas,,0,0,0,,Actually, I'd like coffee instead of tea
Dialogue: 0,0:29:43.00,0:29:43.90,yamadas,,0,0,0,,Oh yeah,
Dialogue: 0,0:29:44.10,0:29:46.42,yamadas,,0,0,0,,when I went just now the bathroom was dirty
Dialogue: 0,0:29:46.85,0:29:48.52,yamadas,,0,0,0,,Make sure to clean it
Dialogue: 0,0:29:48.70,0:29:49.85,yamadas,,0,0,0,,Another thing,
Dialogue: 0,0:29:49.85,0:29:51.85,yamadas,,0,0,0,,when you get groceries, can you pick me up some cigarettes?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:52.87,0:29:55.92,yamadas,,0,0,0,,It's one thing after another with him
Dialogue: 0,0:29:58.75,0:29:59.97,yamadas,,0,0,0,,Dear?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:00.45,0:30:01.97,yamadas,,0,0,0,,Dear?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:04.45,0:30:05.72,yamadas,,0,0,0,, Where's mom?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:05.72,0:30:07.95,yamadas,,0,0,0,,She went to pachinko
Dialogue: 0,0:30:09.07,0:30:12.87,yamadas,,0,0,0,,Kuwata's only given up one run in five games
Dialogue: 0,0:30:13.05,0:30:15.42,yamadas,,0,0,0,,Kuwata throws the pitch
Dialogue: 0,0:30:15.42,0:30:16.20,yamadas,,0,0,0,,It's a hit!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:18.00,0:30:19.47,yamadas,,0,0,0,,It's up and to the right
Dialogue: 0,0:30:19.90,0:30:22.37,yamadas,,0,0,0,,Takahashi makes the catch
Dialogue: 0,0:30:22.37,0:30:23.72,yamadas,,0,0,0,,That's three outs
Dialogue: 0,0:30:23.90,0:30:25.10,yamadas,,0,0,0,,８回の裏
Dialogue: 0,0:30:25.10,0:30:29.82,yamadas,,0,0,0,,ジャイアンツは一番の西からの攻？？ということになるわけです
Dialogue: 0,0:30:29.97,0:30:32.30,yamadas,,0,0,0,,Tonight's broadcast is brought you by...
Dialogue: 0,0:30:32.80,0:30:35.75,yamadas,,0,0,0,,Perfect! It's just starting now
Dialogue: 0,0:30:40.20,0:30:43.07,yamadas,,0,0,0,,Kuwata's defense is great, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:43.32,0:30:45.05,yamadas,,0,0,0,,Yes, truly great
Dialogue: 0,0:30:45.75,0:30:46.72,yamadas,,0,0,0,,It's not over yet
Dialogue: 0,0:30:46.72,0:30:49.17,yamadas,,0,0,0,,Oh but I was looking forward to watching it
Dialogue: 0,0:30:49.57,0:30:50.50,yamadas,,0,0,0,,No way!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:50.65,0:30:52.50,yamadas,,0,0,0,,I want to watch the movie!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:54.32,0:30:56.57,yamadas,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:31:25.10,0:31:27.37,yamadas,,0,0,0,,You can't even watch TV
Dialogue: 0,0:31:27.47,0:31:29.60,yamadas,,0,0,0,,This is better than TV
Dialogue: 0,0:31:45.52,0:31:47.87,yamadas,,0,0,0,,I got it!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:44.42,0:32:46.17,yamadas,,0,0,0,,Hey Noboru
Dialogue: 0,0:32:46.60,0:32:48.17,yamadas,,0,0,0,,Wanna play catch?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:49.20,0:32:49.85,yamadas,,0,0,0,,Sure
Dialogue: 0,0:32:49.87,0:32:51.37,yamadas,,0,0,0,,Father-son talk
Dialogue: 0,0:32:51.37,0:32:53.37,yamadas,,0,0,0,,Don't Enter
Dialogue: 0,0:32:57.65,0:32:58.97,yamadas,,0,0,0,,Wait a sec
Dialogue: 0,0:32:59.25,0:33:01.72,yamadas,,0,0,0,,Usually the parent catches, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:01.87,0:33:03.22,yamadas,,0,0,0,,You're a loud one, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:06.12,0:33:07.07,yamadas,,0,0,0,, Let's go
Dialogue: 0,0:33:07.37,0:33:08.62,yamadas,,0,0,0,,This is a curveball
Dialogue: 0,0:33:08.97,0:33:10.35,yamadas,,0,0,0,,This is a screwball
Dialogue: 0,0:33:10.55,0:33:12.15,yamadas,,0,0,0,,This is a fastball
Dialogue: 0,0:33:12.52,0:33:14.22,yamadas,,0,0,0,,Isn't he annoying
Dialogue: 0,0:33:14.72,0:33:17.62,yamadas,,0,0,0,,Ready? Two outs, bases loaded, you're the relief pitcher
Dialogue: 0,0:33:17.62,0:33:20.45,yamadas,,0,0,0,,No way, I'm a starting pitcher
Dialogue: 0,0:33:20.45,0:33:21.95,yamadas,,0,0,0,,Annoying, aren't they?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:22.40,0:33:24.02,yamadas,,0,0,0,,What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:24.02,0:33:26.55,yamadas,,0,0,0,,野球部じゃピッチャーなんか
Dialogue: 0,0:33:26.55,0:33:28.70,yamadas,,0,0,0,,That's why I should pitch the whole game
Dialogue: 0,0:33:30.62,0:33:32.67,yamadas,,0,0,0,,Alright, that makes sense
Dialogue: 0,0:33:33.05,0:33:34.82,yamadas,,0,0,0,,Let's try to pitch the whole game
Dialogue: 0,0:33:34.97,0:33:37.85,yamadas,,0,0,0,,But...two outs bases loaded
Dialogue: 0,0:33:55.65,0:33:56.82,yamadas,,0,0,0,,Let's go
Dialogue: 0,0:34:02.35,0:34:04.42,yamadas,,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:34:07.80,0:34:09.22,yamadas,,0,0,0,, Dad, what are you listening to?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:11.92,0:34:16.02,yamadas,,0,0,0,,If you listen to this tape over and over your English will improve
Dialogue: 0,0:34:19.25,0:34:21.10,yamadas,,0,0,0,,Isn't that a little naive?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:21.25,0:34:22.90,yamadas,,0,0,0,,In my experience,
Dialogue: 0,0:34:22.90,0:34:24.02,yamadas,,0,0,0,,you need to study
Dialogue: 0,0:34:24.02,0:34:25.05,yamadas,,0,0,0,,you need to study
Dialogue: 0,0:34:25.05,0:34:25.87,yamadas,,0,0,0,,you need to study
Dialogue: 0,0:34:25.87,0:34:26.90,yamadas,,0,0,0,,you need to study
Dialogue: 0,0:34:26.90,0:34:27.77,yamadas,,0,0,0,,you need to study
Dialogue: 0,0:34:27.77,0:34:28.67,yamadas,,0,0,0,,you need to study
Dialogue: 0,0:34:28.67,0:34:29.42,yamadas,,0,0,0,,you need to study
Dialogue: 0,0:34:29.42,0:34:30.15,yamadas,,0,0,0,,you need to study
Dialogue: 0,0:34:30.15,0:34:30.95,yamadas,,0,0,0,,you need to study
Dialogue: 0,0:34:31.00,0:34:31.67,yamadas,,0,0,0,,you need to study
Dialogue: 0,0:34:31.67,0:34:32.40,yamadas,,0,0,0,,you need to study
Dialogue: 0,0:34:32.40,0:34:33.10,yamadas,,0,0,0,,you need to study
Dialogue: 0,0:34:33.10,0:34:37.45,yamadas,,0,0,0,,study, study, study, study, study
Dialogue: 0,0:34:37.47,0:34:42.10,yamadas,,0,0,0,,study, study, study, study, study
Dialogue: 0,0:34:42.10,0:34:46.60,yamadas,,0,0,0,,study, study, study, study, study
Dialogue: 0,0:34:46.60,0:34:48.05,yamadas,,0,0,0,,study, study, study
Dialogue: 0,0:34:48.25,0:34:49.47,yamadas,,0,0,0,,study!
Dialogue: 0,0:34:50.17,0:34:52.00,yamadas,,0,0,0,,全然やる気にならないよ
Dialogue: 0,0:34:52.25,0:34:53.35,yamadas,,0,0,0,,一緒にすんな
Dialogue: 0,0:34:59.52,0:35:01.55,yamadas,,0,0,0,,Want to try a little sake?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:01.77,0:35:02.27,yamadas,,0,0,0,,Sure
Dialogue: 0,0:35:02.37,0:35:03.90,yamadas,,0,0,0,,Dear!
Dialogue: 0,0:35:12.22,0:35:13.75,yamadas,,0,0,0,,How is it? No good?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:16.35,0:35:18.12,yamadas,,0,0,0,,It's dry, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:18.82,0:35:19.87,yamadas,,0,0,0,,What'd you say?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:20.02,0:35:21.60,yamadas,,0,0,0,,Well, I...
Dialogue: 0,0:35:22.70,0:35:23.52,yamadas,,0,0,0,,Why, you little!
Dialogue: 0,0:35:25.20,0:35:26.27,yamadas,,0,0,0,,Noboru!
Dialogue: 0,0:35:26.27,0:35:27.52,yamadas,,0,0,0,,Noboru!
Dialogue: 0,0:35:36.87,0:35:37.72,yamadas,,0,0,0,,Hey Noboru
Dialogue: 0,0:35:38.15,0:35:39.95,yamadas,,0,0,0,,Shall we play catch?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:41.40,0:35:42.42,yamadas,,0,0,0,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:43.67,0:35:45.07,yamadas,,0,0,0,, What do you mean 'why'?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:45.55,0:35:48.10,yamadas,,0,0,0,,For a little father-son talk, as they say
Dialogue: 0,0:35:49.15,0:35:51.22,yamadas,,0,0,0,,In that case we don't have to play catch, do we?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:51.67,0:35:54.37,yamadas,,0,0,0,,Well, that's true, but
Dialogue: 0,0:35:55.15,0:35:58.67,yamadas,,0,0,0,, The environment is also important
Dialogue: 0,0:35:59.30,0:36:01.10,yamadas,,0,0,0,,It's OK. It's too much trouble
Dialogue: 0,0:36:16.12,0:36:18.97,yamadas,,0,0,0,,Kids these days...
Dialogue: 0,0:36:25.35,0:36:28.20,yamadas,,0,0,0,,深刻な親子の断絶やな That kind of relationship is going extinct
Dialogue: 0,0:36:32.02,0:36:34.02,yamadas,,0,0,0,,父権の回復
Dialogue: 0,0:36:37.60,0:36:39.80,yamadas,,0,0,0,,Noboru! You don't put rice into miso soup!
Dialogue: 0,0:36:39.80,0:36:41.37,yamadas,,0,0,0,,You know better!
Dialogue: 0,0:36:42.25,0:36:44.52,yamadas,,0,0,0,,You put the miso soup into the rice.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:47.05,0:36:48.75,yamadas,,0,0,0,,I disagree
Dialogue: 0,0:36:50.20,0:36:51.97,yamadas,,0,0,0,,Why? What's the problem?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:52.40,0:36:54.25,yamadas,,0,0,0,,Do what you want, then
Dialogue: 0,0:36:59.52,0:37:00.65,yamadas,,0,0,0,,Look,
Dialogue: 0,0:37:00.65,0:37:03.52,yamadas,,0,0,0,,You put the water into the cement!
Dialogue: 0,0:37:08.05,0:37:10.60,yamadas,,0,0,0,,Don't hover with your chopsticks over the food. It's rude
Dialogue: 0,0:37:11.72,0:37:14.25,yamadas,,0,0,0,,When you've decided on something, take it with purpose
Dialogue: 0,0:37:15.80,0:37:17.75,yamadas,,0,0,0,,That's my plate
Dialogue: 0,0:37:18.40,0:37:19.42,yamadas,,0,0,0,,Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:20.25,0:37:22.92,yamadas,,0,0,0,,返しなさんな　食べさしを
Dialogue: 0,0:37:28.30,0:37:31.30,yamadas,,0,0,0,,Dad, I need to think of my free research topic
Dialogue: 0,0:37:31.52,0:37:32.82,yamadas,,0,0,0,,What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:33.20,0:37:35.82,yamadas,,0,0,0,,If it's a free topic, can't you choose anything you like?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:36.07,0:37:39.60,yamadas,,0,0,0,,That's true, but I can't come up with anything
Dialogue: 0,0:37:40.42,0:37:42.77,yamadas,,0,0,0,,You can do anything, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:42.72,0:37:44.30,yamadas,,0,0,0,,Yeah, anything
Dialogue: 0,0:37:44.30,0:37:45.42,yamadas,,0,0,0,,Well,
Dialogue: 0,0:37:46.42,0:37:49.92,yamadas,,0,0,0,,If you told me "you can write about anything you want"
Dialogue: 0,0:37:49.92,0:37:51.92,yamadas,,0,0,0,,I'd draw a blank too
Dialogue: 0,0:37:52.07,0:37:53.92,yamadas,,0,0,0,,That's what I'm saying.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:55.00,0:37:56.35,yamadas,,0,0,0,,Anything, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:06.62,0:38:10.95,yamadas,,0,0,0,,What should you do? Anything?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:15.77,0:38:17.42,yamadas,,0,0,0,,Sought after freedom
Dialogue: 0,0:38:18.17,0:38:20.25,yamadas,,0,0,0,,The freedom of your dreams
Dialogue: 0,0:38:20.37,0:38:23.97,yamadas,,0,0,0,,Freedom that's finally held out in front of you
Dialogue: 0,0:38:28.27,0:38:30.47,yamadas,,0,0,0,,but you don't know what to do
Dialogue: 0,0:38:36.20,0:38:38.32,yamadas,,0,0,0,,He turned into a philosopher
Dialogue: 0,0:38:38.65,0:38:42.07,yamadas,,0,0,0,,He's just thinking about retirement
Dialogue: 0,0:38:42.70,0:38:44.67,yamadas,,0,0,0,,親父の背中
Dialogue: 0,0:38:44.67,0:38:46.67,yamadas,,0,0,0,,
